high_descs: Pick up the lettuce that is on the far left.
Turn to your right and walk up to the marble sink.
Rinse the lettuce in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn completely around and head over to the fridge.
Place the lettuce to the right of the bowl and close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean piece of lettuce into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the wooden table.
Pick up the leftmost head of lettuce off of the table.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the head of lettuce in the sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean head of lettuce.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the clean head of lettuce on the top shelf of the right side.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the sink
Pick up lettuce from the table
Move to the sink to the right
Clean the lettuce in the sink with water and pick back up
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Put the lettuce inside and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put cleaned lettuce in the fridge.
